<% const bttsDays = [{key:'jana', label:'Jana'}, {key:'leo', label:'Leo'}, {key:'kesho', label:'Kesho'}]; %>
<div class="section-stack">
  <section class="section-card">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div>
        <h1 class="section-title display-6 fw-bold mb-2">Mkeka wa Both Teams to Score</h1>
        <p class="section-subtitle mb-0">Timu zote kufungana (GG)</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="lead">
      Mkeka wa GG/NG au Both Teams to Score (BTTS) ni moja wapo ya mikeka yetu ya kila siku inayofanya vizuri sana.
      Jipatie bashiri za leo na za kila siku za BTTS au GG/NG na uongeze nafasi yako ya ushindi.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="tip-panel section-card" data-tip-category="btts">
      <div
        class="section-header flex-column flex-md-row align-items-start align-items-md-center justify-content-between gap-3 mb-3">
        <div>
          <h2 class="section-title h4 mb-1">Utabiri wa Leo - BTTS</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle mb-0">Chagua siku kuona mikeka yote ya GG/NG</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="nav nav-pills day-toggle" role="tablist">
          <% bttsDays.forEach(({key, label}) => { %>
          <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
            <button class="nav-link text-dark <%= key === 'leo' ? 'active' : '' %>" id="tab-btts-<%= key %>-tab"
              data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#tab-btts-<%= key %>" type="button" role="tab"
              aria-controls="tab-btts-<%= key %>" aria-selected="<%= key === 'leo' ? 'true' : 'false' %>">
              <%= label %>
            </button>
          </li>
          <% }) %>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="tab-content">
        <% bttsDays.forEach(({ key }) => { %>
        <div class="tab-pane fade <%= key === 'leo' ? 'show active' : '' %>" id="tab-btts-<%= key %>" role="tabpanel"
          aria-labelledby="tab-btts-<%= key %>-tab">
          <%- include('../partials/btts-cards', { tips: tips[key] || [] }) %>
        </div>
        <% }) %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-card">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title h4 mb-0">Mwongozo wa Kubashiri Both Teams To Score (GG/NG)</h2>
    </div>

    <p>Utabiri wa <b>Both Teams To Score (BTTS)</b> maarufu kama <b>GG/NG</b> ni moja ya masoko rahisi na nafuu
      kuyabashiri. Ni rahisi kuelewa na haihitaji maelezo mengi... unachotazama ni kama timu zote mbili zitafunga au la
      ndani ya dakika 90.</p>

    <p>GG (Yes) ina maana timu zote mbili zinatakiwa kufunga angalau bao moja kila moja.
      NG (No) ina maana mechi inapaswa kuisha bila mojawapo ya timu kufunga, au hata zote mbili zikikosa.</p>

    <h3 class="section-title h5 mb-1">Jinsi BTTS Inavyofanya Kazi (GG/NG)</h3>

    <p>Tunapozungumzia BTTS, tunatabiri uwezekano wa timu zote mbili kupata mabao. Haijalishi mechi ni ngumu au
      rahisi...
      muhimu ni timu zote kufanikiwa kutikisa nyavu kabla ya mchezo kumalizika.</p>

    <p>Swali kuu la kujiuliza kabla ya kuchagua GG/NG ni: <b>Hizi timu mbili zimekutana mara ngapi na matokeo yao ya
        kawaida
        yamekuwa yapi?</b>
      Majibu yake yanapatikana kupitia takwimu za mechi zao zilizopita, form ya timu, ligi wanazocheza na mashindano
      mbalimbali.</p>

    <h3 class="section-title h5 mb-1">Jinsi ya Kuchagua Mechi Sahihi za GG</h3>

    <p>Ni busara kuchagua mechi zenye nafasi kubwa ya timu zote kufunga, mfano:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Timu zote zina wastani mzuri wa kufunga mabao kwenye mechi zao 5â€“10 zilizopita</li>
      <li>Ulinzi wa timu zote mbili hauna nguvu sana</li>
      <li>Head-to-head zao zinaonyesha mechi zao mara nyingi huwa na magoli kutoka pande zote</li>
      <li>Timu zote zinacheza soka la kushambulia na zina washambuliaji katika form</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Unashauriwa pia kuchagua mechi ambayo angalau timu moja ina asilimia ya juu ya kufunga kuliko nyingine... hii
      hupunguza hatari ya mechi kuisha 0-0 au timu kukosa magoli kabisa.</p>

    <h3 class="section-title h5 mb-1">Mifano ya Matokeo ya GG (Yes)</h3>

    <ul>
      <li>1-1</li>
      <li>2-1, 1-2</li>
      <li>2-2</li>
      <li>3-1, 1-3</li>
      <li>3-2, 2-3</li>
      <li>N.k</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="section-title h5 mb-1">Mifano ya Matokeo ya NG (No)</h3>

    <ul>
      <li>0-0</li>
      <li>1-0, 0-1</li>
      <li>2-0, 0-2</li>
      <li>3-0, 0-3</li>
      <li>4-0, 0-4</li>
      <li>N.k</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Kwa kifupi... GG ni nzuri kwa mechi za ushambuliaji, wakati NG ni bora kwa mechi za ulinzi mkali au timu dhaifu
      dhidi ya timu yenye nguvu. Tumia takwimu sahihi ili kuongeza nafasi za kuchukua ushindi.</p>
  </section>

</div>